+### Upstream Update Workflow
+
+**Purpose:** Automate updating automagik-forge to new upstream versions with mechanical rebranding.
+
+**Usage:**
+```bash
+# Automated via agent
+mcp__genie__run agent="utilities/upstream-update" prompt="Update to v0.0.106"
+```
+
+**What It Does:**
+1. Fetches specified version from upstream submodule
+2. Runs mechanical rebrand script (`scripts/rebrand.sh`)
+3. Verifies zero vibe-kanban references remain
+4. Validates build success (cargo check + pnpm check)
+5. Prepares changes for commit
+
+**Verification:**
+- All vibe-kanban references replaced → automagik-forge
+- Application builds successfully
+- Tests pass (cargo test --workspace)
+- Ready to commit with descriptive message
+
+**Manual Alternative:**
+```bash
+cd upstream && git fetch origin && git checkout v0.0.106 && cd ..
+./scripts/rebrand.sh
+grep -r "vibe-kanban" upstream frontend | wc -l  # Must be 0
+cargo check --workspace && cd frontend && pnpm run check
+git add -A && git status
+```
+
+**Total time:** ~2 minutes. No manual intervention required.
